reviewText: Well I seen it on the military channel on cable.
I was very pleased with item. would buy from seller again!! This is an awesome series for any history buff.

Interesting stories by WWII veterans.  It gave much insight into the struggles and hardships of war.  You realize that so many paid the price for freedom.  Young boys just out of high school were sent off to war to become fighting men. Many never returned, and those who did who had been in combat had their lives changed forever.
Not the US version, so it has a different and frankly not as good narrator. Still the same excellent interviews with veterans.
EXCELLENT ITEM AND VALUE!  THANK YOU
